---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="模板 — AI PM 工作台" description="AI 产品管理的可复用模板" isEn={false}>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">模板</h1>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-2xl">预构建的模板，加速你的 AI 产品工作流。与工作台配合使用，生成结构化文档。</p>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">AI PM Canvas</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">一个 12 维度的框架，用于对 AI 产品进行结构化思考。适用于编写 PRD 或构建原型之前。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">框架</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">12 个维度</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/canvas/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">查看 Canvas &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">轻量 PRD 模板</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">专为 AI 产品概念优化的最小 PRD 结构。涵盖问题、用户、AI 能力、工作流和评估。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">PRD</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">轻量级</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/ai_prd_lite_template/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">查看模板 &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">案例研究模板</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">将你的 AI 产品项目记录为结构化案例研究。捕捉决策、权衡取舍和经验教训。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">案例研究</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">文档化</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/ai_pm_case_study_template/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">查看模板 &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">工作台文档包</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">由工作台生成：产品简报、工作流规格、评估计划、验收标准、编码智能体交接文档和 CLAUDE.md 初始模板。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">生成</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">6 份文档</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/workbench/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">打开工作台 &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
